  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育平台设计一个完整的数据备份与恢复架构。核心诉求是：ClassroomService、ContentCDN、StudentDB、LMS_Portal 和 GradeSync 这几个服务之间要有清晰的灾备流向。先从数据源层开始吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先把数据源层画成\"Источники данных\"子图，里面放 ClassroomService 和 ContentCDN。这两个是主要的数据产生方，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Источники данных"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ClassroomService 产生课堂互动数据，ContentCDN 承载课程内容。然后需要一个自动备份层，把 ClassroomService 和 StudentDB 的备份任务自动化处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Автоматические бэкапы"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了\"Автоматические бэкапы\"子图，包含 ClassroomService 和 StudentDB。接下来是手动操作层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Автоматические бэкапы"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，手动操作层需要包含 ClassroomService 和 ContentCDN，用于运维人员触发的紧急备份或特殊场景。然后 Storage 层用 StudentDB 和 LMS_Portal 作为存储目标。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Ручные операции",
        "Хранение"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加\"Ручные операции\"和\"Хранение\"两个子图。现在连接关系怎么定？从数据源到备份层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ручные операции",
        "Хранение"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ClassroomService 要分出三条线：一条到自动备份层的 ClassroomService，一条到手动操作的 ClassroomService，还有一条到手动操作的 ContentCDN——因为课堂数据里可能引用 CDN 内容，需要联动备份。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Автоматические бэкапы",
        "Ручные операции"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，A 节点连到 C、E、F。那自动备份层内部呢？ClassroomService 的备份数据存到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "自动备份的 ClassroomService 数据要落入 StudentDB，作为结构化存储。然后 StudentDB 再向下游分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "C 到 D 的连线已添加。接下来 Storage 层的 StudentDB 需要连向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Хранение"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Storage 层的 StudentDB 要连到 LMS_Portal，这是主要的存储归档路径。另外还需要一个恢复层\"Восстановление\"，包含 GradeSync 和 LMS_Portal，用于数据回灌。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Восстановление"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加恢复层子图，G 到 H 的连线也画好了。StudentDB 到恢复层的关系呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Восстановление"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Storage 的 StudentDB 要同时连到恢复层的 GradeSync 和 LMS_Portal，这样成绩数据和课程门户都能独立恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "G 到 I、G 到 J 都连上了。顶层还需要 Data、Backup、Storage 这三个汇总节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data",
        "Backup",
        "Storage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要，作为概念层：Data 流向 Backup，Backup 再流向 Storage，形成总览。不过检查一下，手动操作层的 ContentCDN 是不是还没上游？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data",
        "Backup",
